column1: Baby Barnaby's////Being in a somewhat healthy mood
column2: i went for the high protein burrito
column3: but i substituted my tomatoes with their potatoes (which the waitress was more than happy to do).  The eggs in the burrito were amazing... so fluffy
column4: flavorful and buttery - i cant imagine how that thing was healthy.  The potatoes also had the right crisp outside and warm soft inside.
